cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite the accompanying paper."
type: software
title: "ForeFlow Agents Engine"
abstract: >
  Operational infrastructure for running five Foresight Arena forecasting
  agents (foreflow-ensemble, foreflow-debate, foreflow-orchestrator,
  foreflow-pipeline, foreflow-consensus). Provides wallet registration,
  cron-based scheduling, healthchecks, and VPS deployment tooling for
  "Coordination as an Architectural Layer for LLM-Based Multi-Agent Systems".
